name: OSLogEntryLog.Level
desc: The log level at which the entry was generated.

items.name: case undefined
items.desc: The log level was never specified.

items.name: case debug
items.desc: A log level that captures diagnostic information.

items.name: case info
items.desc: The log level that captures additional information.

items.name: case notice
items.desc: The log level that captures notifications.

items.name: case error
items.desc: The log level that captures errors.

items.name: case fault
items.desc: The log level that captures fault information.
